Twisted Runner 12.1.0 (2012-06-02)
==================================

Deprecations and Removals
-------------------------
 - ProcessMonitor.active, consistencyDelay, and consistency in
   twisted.runner.procmon were deprecated since 10.1 have been
   removed. (#5517)


